OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry start this morning, some
OL,6,Fearly brightness in the east.
OL,7,FOtherwise cloudy with outbreaks of
OL,8,Frain spreading southeast for a time.
OL,9,FDrier and brighter in the southwest
OL,10,Flater. Mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA few showers this evening.
OL,13,FThen the rest of the night will be dry
OL,14,Fwith clear periods and just the odd
OL,15,Fshower. Cold with patchy frost.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FMost of the day will be dry,
OL,18,Fsome early brightness. Outbreaks of
OL,19,Frain spreading east from late
OL,20,Fafternoon into the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
