OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FRain at
OL,6,Ffirst on Friday then drier with a few
OL,7,Fshowers. Cloudy on Saturday with rain,
OL,8,Foccasionally heavy, spreading east.
OL,9,FCold and bright on Sunday with
OL,10,Fblustery showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
